	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok Since no-one has posted on this Topic, and I jsut got my Book about half an hour ago, I'll let you know how to do it.&nbsp;&nbsp;I went in there with a big raid and figured that was the way to do it, i was wrong.<br>All you need is one group, A Wizzy, a Necro or a Cleric, and yourself. that's it that's all, you can't gate on the Plane of Sky so you're going to die once.  <br>The wizzy needs to go to Erudin and pick up a spell component for the port, once you get up there, you need to buy a &quot;Key of Veesheen&quot; (I think) from the &quot;Key Master&quot; it looks like a Jade and only costs 1 cp.  Then you need to attack him, I think he had a AE attack so have everyone else stand back, I'm not too sure about the AE thing since i was dead, but that's what people said.  <br>Next the Cleric is going to res you, once you get back to the Plane of Sky ONLY LOOT THE KEY!!<br>Once you have the key go around and click it on the ports till you get ported to the Quest room, all of the mobs in the quest room and the first Island con indiff so you have nothing to worry about anything attacking you.  go in grab the Book, and have the cleric res you again, and you're done.<br>Now all you have to do is walk off of the Island and you will land in the harbour of Freeport, don't worry you won't die, it's actually kind of fun.<br>Well good luck on the rest of your Epic, now I need to go and get a few more pieces of my own.<br><br>Peppwyl<br>Lvl 55 Enchanter<br>Terew Marr<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
